OL,3,CHome Office launches social media
OL,4,Ccampaign in Vietnam to deter illegal
OL,5,Cmigrants
OL,7,FSocial media adverts aimed at
OL,8,Fdeterring migrants from coming to the
OL,9,FUK illegally have been launched by the
OL,10,FHome Office as part of a new campaign.
OL,12,FThe drive, which begins on Monday,
OL,13,Fwill use adverts on Facebook and
OL,14,FYouTube to target people in the
OL,15,Fsoutheast Asian country who may be
OL,16,Fconsidering making illegal journeys to
OL,17,Fthe UK.
