OL,7,FAn increasing proportion of small boat
OL,8,Fmigrants are Vietnamese and they are
OL,9,Fone of the top 10 nationalities for
OL,10,Fmigrants crossing the Channel
OL,11,Fillegally, the Home Office said.
OL,13,FThe department added that the adverts
OL,14,Fwill "set out the risks of being
OL,15,Findebted to and exploited by the
OL,16,Fpeople-smuggling gangs who profit from
OL,17,Ffacilitating small boat crossings".
