OL,4,Ccampaign in Vietnam to deter illegal
OL,5,Cmigrants
OL,7,FThe campaign will also warn
OL,8,Fprospective Vietnamese migrants of the
OL,9,F"reality of living in the UK illegally
OL,10,Fwith no right to be in the UK and no
OL,11,Faccess to public services or funding",
OL,12,Fand use "real testimonies from those
OL,13,Fwho regret coming to the UK illegally".
OL,15,FIn one advert, a migrant shares his
OL,16,Fexperience of sleeping in a camp in
OL,17,FCalais for five nights under the
OL,18,Fsupervision of armed guards, before
OL,19,Ftaking the journey across the Channel
OL,20,Ffrom France to the UK.
