OL,7,FThe migrant, referred to as K, says in
OL,8,Fthe advert: "Never again would I risk
OL,9,Fmy life in a small boat, even if you
OL,10,Fbribed me."
OL,12,FVietnamese social media users will
OL,13,Falso be directed by the campaign to a
OL,14,Fnew website featuring videos from
OL,15,FBorder Force officers describing
OL,16,F"shocking cases" and their experiences
OL,17,Fof "rescuing small boat migrants from
OL,18,Flife-threatening danger in the
OL,19,FChannel".
