OL,7,FThe Home Office said the launch ,
OL,8,Fadding that similar campaigns were
OL,9,F"also being considered for other
OL,10,Fpriority countries".
OL,12,FHome Secretary James Cleverly said:
OL,13,F"This is a powerful campaign which
OL,14,Fdemonstrates first-hand that life for
OL,15,Fpeople arriving here illegally is a
OL,16,Ffar cry from the lies they have been
OL,17,Fsold by the gangs on the other side of
OL,18,Fthe Channel.
