OL,3,CHome Office launches social media
OL,4,Ccampaign in Vietnam to deter illegal
OL,5,Cmigrants
OL,7,F"Last year, similar work contributed
OL,8,Fto a 90% reduction in small boat
OL,9,Farrivals from Albania, and overall
OL,10,Fnumbers are down by a third, but there
OL,11,Fis more to do.
OL,13,F"Expanding our campaign to Vietnam,
OL,14,Fanother key partner in our work to
OL,15,Ftackle illegal migration, will help us
OL,16,Fto save more lives and dent the
OL,17,Fbusiness model of the criminals who
OL,18,Fprofit from this vile trade."
