OL,5,Cmigrants
OL,7,FUK and Vietnamese authorities "already
OL,8,Fwork closely" to prevent illegal
OL,9,Fjourneys to the UK and remove those
OL,10,Fwith no right to be in the country,
OL,11,Faccording to the Home Office.
OL,13,FThe department added that senior
OL,14,Fofficials from the UK and Vietnam are
OL,15,Fdue to meet in London on April 17, to
OL,16,F"discuss working in even closer
OL,17,Fpartnership on migration issues".
